{"tid":1444522,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家有無諗過點解民陣唔搞多次和理非大遊行","createTime":"2019-08-11T12:41:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T14:27:54.000Z","uid":207710,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"be83e88a894c31624ad08ffafb08bcfed84ebf58","tid":1444522,"uid":207710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:41:35.000Z","msg":"當然可能係驚少人過之前<br />\n但亦可能係<br />\n呢個時勢，警方根本唔會批出不反對通知書<br />\n即使搞手係民陣<br />\n當然無不反對通知書都可以自發自己遊行<br />\n但未聚人，警方就會開始驅散<br />\n有驅散行動，就無可能可以保持到和理非<br />\n呢個就係部分理想主義者無諗到嘅盲點<br />\n所以唔係大家唔想回歸和理非唞唞<br />\n而係根本時勢唔同咗，你未聚200萬人佢已經封站出旗<br />\n幫推, thx"},{"pid":"0f98085871910d1c51f2a191d776307a0d5e9edc","tid":1444522,"uid":207710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:42:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a577a0041c4b602515ca856e4135c9172553d32a","tid":1444522,"uid":207710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:43:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"66b6f30d1e828e1b999cd29742a6685d92a00dbe","tid":1444522,"uid":207710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:43:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b36880b4c99b456f978621baadfe876b52dede4e","tid":1444522,"uid":207710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:44:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bbb2451796df315424f302c65d98b9363de3a5c2","tid":1444522,"uid":207710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:44:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"efcbf96ee8f15a67423e87cac57136385b4d5a4d","tid":1444522,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:44:35.000Z","msg":"啱"},{"pid":"32087ef93260e6bfe2e66653dc136a0a7a141f7d","tid":1444522,"uid":277323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:45:29.000Z","msg":"班仆街怕死'"},{"pid":"d9fd433448c45501a8599b1a84b7f3cc03c75b7c","tid":1444522,"uid":9369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:46:30.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"997af8a9bcf164364